Type: Package
Package: y2pareto
Title: Convenience functions to make the 80% of data preparation faster
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person('Scott', 'Riding', email = "scott@y2analytics.com", role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Maintainer: Scott Riding <scott@y2analytics.com>
Description: Convenience functions for converting and recoding data into the
    right formats to execute analysis and visualization at Y2 Analytics.
    These functions fall into two categories: 1) conversion functions, generally
    used to convert data from an SPSS labelled format into something more useful
    to us, and 2) recoding functions, generally used to combined a given 
    column into a new categorization schema.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.1)
Imports:
    tidyverse (>= 1.1.1),
    labelled (>= 1.0.0),
    forcats (>= 0.2.0)
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
